#Alice is driving from her home to her office which is A kilometers away and will take her X hours to reach. Bob is driving from his home to his office which is 
B kilometers away and will take him Y hours to reach. Determine who is driving faster, else, if they are both driving at the same speed print EQUAL.



t=int(input())
for i in range(t):
    A,X,B,Y=map(int,input().split())
    a=A/X
    b=B/Y 
    if a>b:
        print("ALICE")
    elif b>a:
        print("BOB")
    else:
        print("EQUAL")
